Title: Suspiciously Quiet
Description:
Can you spare a minute, $n? I haven't heard from my two apprentices, Scrumpy and Tucky, in some time. 

This is concerning. 

I sent them to fetch us supplies for the inn. They couldn't have strayed too far...

Please find them, but I warn you... They're... quite the handful.
ObjectivesText: Find Noriko's apprentices in Camp Antonidas.
